# Browser Maps key — repo ROOT only (not backend/.env). Restart Vite after edits.
# Cloud Console: Maps JavaScript API + Places API (New); restrict key by HTTP referrer http://localhost:5173/*
#
VITE_GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY=
# Optional fallback name (vite.config merges into VITE_): GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY=

# Quick check: http://localhost:5173/maps-demo.html — npm run demo:maps
